In all the [Standard Headhunting], if you have not obtained any 6-star Operator after 50 rolls, the odds of getting 6-star Operators will be increased from 2% to 4% in the next roll; And if you still have not obtained any 6-star Operator in the 51st roll, the odds will be increased from 4% to 6% in the next roll. [P.S.] If you have obtained any one 6-star Operator in an event, the odds of getting 6-star Operators will be reduced to 2% in all events.
